data.content:
Danh từ
sự làm đúng theo (một yêu cầu, một mệnh lệnh), sự tuân thủ
it was done in compliance of your wish
cái đó đã được làm đúng theo ý muốn của anh
(thường xấu) sự phục tùng, sự khúm núm

noun
[noncount] formal :the act or process of doing what you have been asked or ordered to do :the act or process of complying
She was rewarded for her compliance.
There has been a low/high rate of compliance with the new law.
in compliance with
in the way that is required by (a rule, law, etc.)
In compliance with a court order, the company has ceased operations.
The workers were not in full compliance with the rules. [=were not following the rules exactly]
